  Lun7 siat bok8-chu2 kap che3 bok8-chu2 e5 m7-tioh8. TaN kou2-cha2 lang5 siat bok8-chu2 che3-su7, sui-bong2 si7 beh hou7 lang5 ki3-liam7, iau2-ku2 iah8 si7 m7-tioh8. In-ui7 che3-su7 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 siat, hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 thang hian3-che3 lai5 siok8 choe7. Lang5 chi2-u7 thang che3 ti7 Siong7-te3; na7 eng7 chit-e5 le2-sou3 khi3 che3 thiN-toe7, kui2-sin5, bok8-chu2, che si7 chhiam3-koan5 lam7-sam2, put-chi2 tek-choe7 Siong7-te3. Koh iah8 si7 hoan7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 kai3-lut8; Siong7-te3 e5 kai3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 i2- goa7, m7-thang u7 pat8-e5 Siong7-te3; bok8-tit tiau-khek ngou2-siong7.¡¨ Lang5 chhai7 bok8- chu2, si7 hoan7-tioh8 chit-e5 kai3. M7-tan7-na7 an2-ni, iah8 si7 hoan7-tioh8 Tiong-kok e5 kou2- le2. Chiau3 Tiong-kok e5 kou2-le2, tok8-tok8 tioh8 Hong5-te3 kap chu-hou5 chiah oe7 chhai7-tit bok8-chu2, peh-siN3-lang5 long2 boe7 tit-thang chhai7 bok8-chu2, iah8 boe7 tit- thang khi2 chou2-bio7. Koh Hong5-te3 chiah oe7 che3 tit chhit-tai7 e5 chou2, chu-hou5 oe7 che3 tit gou7-tai7 e5 chou2; peh-siN3 chi2-u7 oe7 tit-thang che3 i e5 pe7-bu2 tiaN7-tiaN7. 
  Kau3 Beng5-tiau5 chiah koh tiaN7-tioh8 peh-siN3 iah8 oe7 tit-thang che3 kau3 saN-tai7 e5 chou2, na7-si7 chit-tiap8 e5 peh-siN3-lang5, chhiam3-koan5 khi2 chou2-bio7, chhai7 bok8-chu2, che3 kau3 kui2 chap8 tai7; che m7-tan7-na7 si7 bo5 chiau3 to7-li2, iah8 si7 bo5 chiau3 le2-sou3. Koh lang5 chhai7 bok8-chu2, hoan2-tng2 si7 siat-tok8--tioh8 chou2-kong tiaN7-tiaN7. In-ui7 bok8-chu2 si7 chha5-pang, kap-choh-tiam3 sou2 eng7 chhiu2 siN--e5; lang5 chiong kui2-e5 chiN5 chhin3-chhai2 khi3 boe2 chit8-sian lai5, chiu7 ho7-choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong. Siat-su2 chou2-kong oe7 chai, kiam2 m7 put-chi2 toa7 siu7- khi3 mah? ChhiaN2 eng7 phi3-ju7 lai5 kong2. Cheng-siN pi2 chhiu7-bak8 si7 khah kui3-khi3; lang5 liah8 cheng-siN choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong, chiu7 lan2 tek-khak toa7 siu7-khi3; iah8 lan2 ka-ki7 liah8 chha5-pang choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong, m7-chai-kio3 si7 leng5-jiok8 chou2-kong, che-si7 toa7 chho3-gou7. Cha2 u7 chit8-chiah Tai7-Eng kok e5 chun5 khi3 In3-tou7 kok, chhau3-tu2-kham2 u7 chit8-chiah chiau2 pe lai5, hioh ti7 ui5 teng2; chun5-chu2 bong2 eng7 chheng3 ka7 i phah--si2. Liam5-piN In3- tou7 e5 lang5 long2 ui5-lui5 lai5, m7 pang3 i soah. Chun5-chu2 mng7 si7 siaN2-su7; hia-e5 lang5 in3 kong2, ¡§Li2 tiN3 m7-chai, li2 tu2-a2 phah-si2 e5 chiau2 si7 goan2 e5 chou2-kong.¡¨ Chun5-chu2 iah8 kiaN, iah8 ho2 chhio3; chiah siuN7 chit8-e5 ke3 ka2-chia3 kong2, ¡§Na7-si7 an2-ni, chiu7 goa2 bo5 m7-tioh8; goa2 ti7 goan2 kok nih8, goan2 chou2 si2, khi3 piN3 choe3 hi5, khit lin2 e5 chou2 teh khi3 chiah8. Sou2-i2 goa2 jip8 kau3 chia, thoe3-goan2 chou2 po3 siu5; an2-ni, lin2 chou2 chiah8 goan2 e5 chou2, goa2 phah si2 lin2 e5 chou2, kiam2 m7 hap8-gi5 mah?¡¨ Hia-e5 lang5 bo5 oe7 thang in3, chiah khi3. TaN m7-chai Tiong- kok lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-e5 tai7-chi3, phah- sng3 In3-tou7 lang5 si7 tioh8 a2 m7-tioh8. Goa2 phah-sng3 tak8-lang5 long2 si7 chhio3 i cho3 gong7, na7-si7 i sui-bong2 si7 gong7, iau2-ku2 si7 liah8 oah8 chiau2 choe3 i e5 chou2-kong; iah8 lan2 koh si7 liah8 si2-si2 e5 chhiu7-chha5 lai5 choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong, m7-chai pi2 In3-tou7 lang5 khah ti3-sek a2-si7 khah gong7? 
  Lun7 bok8-chu2 tek-khak bo5-iaN2 u7 sin5. Chiau3 Seng3-chheh e5 to7-li2, lang5 chhut-si3 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 i sin5-hun5; kau3 si2 chiu7 tioh8 hoan2-pun2, seng-khu iu5-goan5 kui thou5, sin5-hun5 liam5-piN kau3 Siong7-te3 tau siu7 sim2-phoaN3; ho2--e5 eng2-oan2 tiam3 thian-tong5, phaiN2--e5 eng2-oan2 kui toe7-gak8; beh thai2 u7 koh sim2-mih8 sin5-hun5 lai5 tiam3 ti7 bok8-chu2--nih8, ia7-si7 bong7--nih8? Chiu7 pun2-kok e5 keng-su ia7 kong2: ¡§ Lang5 si2 chiu7 kui chiuN7 thiN, seng-khu kui toe7; sou2-i2 ho2 si2 choe3 chou2-lok8.¡¨ Koh kong2: ¡§Oah8 si7 chhut-goa7, si2 si7 to2--khi3;¡¨ TaN i2-keng kong2 to2-khi3, chiu7 tek-khak bo5 koh lai5 tiam3 ti7 bok8-chu2--nih8 si7 beng5. Koh Si-keng kong2: ¡§Bun5-ong5 si2-liau2, khi3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 sin-piN.¡¨ Tui3 an2-ni khoaN3, Tiong-kok e5 chheh ia7 u7 beng5-beng5 kong2, lang5 i2-keng si2-liau2 sin5-hun5 bo5 koh u7 tiam3 ti7 se3-kan e5 tai7-chi3. 
  Koh eng7 hian7-si5 e5 lang5 sou2 tui3-tiong7-- e5, lai5 kan-cheng3 in. Chhin-chhiuN7 choe3 kong-tek e5 tai7-chi3, si7 kong2, ¡§Lang5 long2 u7 choe7, si2 tioh8 loh8 te7-gek8; sou2-i2 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 lai5 choe3 kong-tek, phah te7-gek8, chhiau-tou7 i-e5 chou2-kong khi3 chhut-si3.¡¨ TaN i2-keng kong2 i-e5 chou2-kong ti7 te7-gek8-- nih8, chiu7 chaiN2-iuN7 koh kong2 u7 tiam3 ti7 bok8-chu2--nih8? I2-keng chhiau-tou7 i khi3 chhut-si3, chiu7 chaiN2-iuN7 iau2-ku2 ti7 chou2- bio7--nih8 teh che3-su7? Che long2 si7 ka-ki7 saN mau5-tun2 e5 tai7-chi3, si7 lang5 long2 bo5 siuN7, lam7-sam2 gong7-gong7 choe3 tiaN7-tiaN7. U7 lang5 kong2, ¡§Lang5 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5-hun5, chit8-tiau5 ti7 bong7--nih8, chit8-tiau5 ti7 bok8- chu2--nih8, chit8-tiau5 khi3 chhut-si3.¡¨ Na7-si7 che si7 Hut8-kau3 lam7-sam2 e5 oe7, Tiong-kok e5 keng-tian2 long2 bo5 kong2, tek-khak si7 bo5 iaN2 e5 tai7-chi3. TaN goa2 beh pian7-lun7. Siat-su2 lang5 na7 chin-chiaN3 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5- hun5, chiu7 siN-cheng5 tek-khak toa7 boe7 peng5-an, iah8 si2-au7 tek-khak toa7 saN-chiN. In-ui7 lang5 teh choe3 tai7-chi3, si7 sin5-hun5 teh chu2-i3; taN tak8 lang5 na7 u7 saN-tiau5 e5 sin5-hun5, chiu7 tang5-si5 chit8-tiau5 chu2-i3 beh khun3, chit8-tiau5 chu2-i3 beh thit-tho5, chit8 tiau5 chu2-i3 beh chiah8; taN beh chaiN2-iuN7? Siat-su2 si2 na7 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5-hun5, chiu7 tah-loh8 chit8-tiau5 beh khi3 tai5 ti7 bong7-lai7, tah-loh8 chit8-tiau5 beh khi3 siu7 te7-gek8 e5 heng5-hoat8? Tek-khak si7 saN-chiN beh khi3 toa3 ti7 bok8-chu2--nih8, khah hu3-kui3. Chit-ho7 kau3-kek8 bo5 li2 e5 oe7, lang5 iau2-ku2 khi3 sin3--i, sit8-chai7 si7 kho2-sioh. 
  Se3-siok8 e5 lang5 siong5-siong5 kiaN na7-bo5 chhai7 bok8-chu2, bo5 che3-su7, chiu7 oe7 hou7 chou2-kong khian3-chek, sou2-i2 goa2 ai3 koh gi7- lun7 chit chat. TaN thiN-toe7 ban7 hang7 mih8 long2-si7 Siong7-te3 chiang2-koan2--e5, lang5 e5 si2, oah8, chai-e7, hok-khi3, iah8 long2-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 liau7-li2--e5; na7 m7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3, chiu7 bo5 chit8-hang7 mih8 oe7 hou7 lang5 e5 chai-e7, a2-si7 hok-khi3. Ho5-hong3 chou2-kong i2-keng si2, i-e5 sin5-hun5 eng2-oan2 khi3 ti7 i sou2 eng-kai tiam3 e5 sou2-chai7, beh thai3-tho2 oe7 koh lai5 kang3 chai-e7, a2-si7 hok-khi3? Chit-e5 li2 si7 put-chi2 beng5. Chhi3-khoaN3 thiN-e7 ban7-kok, hia-e5 bo5 che3 kui2-sin5, tok8-tok8 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3--e5, hia-e5 kok si7 khah heng-ong7, lang5 iah8 khah chai5-tiau7; iah8 pai3 kui2-sin5--e5, i-e5 kok si7 khah soe-lam2, lang5 iah8 khah gu5- chhun2. Tui3 an2-ni khoaN3 chiu7 thang chai che3-su7 m7-na7 bo5 li7-ek, si7 hoan2-tng2 u7 sun2- hai7. Goa2 siong5-siong5 khoaN3-kiN3 song3- hiong e5 lang5, na7 kau3 ki7-sin5 che3-su7 e5 si5, chiu7 peh-sim hoan5-lo2; siuN7 na7 beh hau3, chin7 bo5 chiN5, na7 m7 hau3, chiu7 kiaN-liau2 oe7 hou7 chou2-kong khian3-chek. Bo5-ta5-tit- oa5, chiu7 tng3 saN, chioh lai7, lai5 boe2 hiuN-chek, pan7 che3-mih8, ti3-kau3 na2 song3-hiong, na2 kan-khou2. Siat-su2 i-e5 chou2-kong na7 u7 siaN3, chiu7 chaiN2-iuN7 kau3 chiah put-cheng5 put-gi7, beh chiah8 i-e5 che3-su7, iah8 long2-bo5 po2-pi3--i? Koh khah ki5-koai3--e5, se3-siok8 u7 chit8-ho7 e5 bo5-su5-tan5; iah8 u7 lang5 ho7- choe3 cheng3-kong-ma2-su5; tai7-seng long2 u7 kiaN2-sun thang hau3, au7-lai5 bo5 lang5, chiah hou7 lang5 chhiaN2 lai5 hiat ti7 bo5-su5- tan5--nih8; chiu7 lang5 iau2-ku2 jiat8-sim teh- keng3-hong7, m7-chai i siong7-chhiaN2 boe7 oe7 po2-pi3 i-e5 kiaN2-sun, hou7 i-e5 kiaN2-sun si2 kau3 bo5 lang5, ho5-hong3 beh thai2-oe7 po2-pi3 pat8- lang5? Che si7 lang5 chin gong7 kau3 kek8. Tui3 an2-ni khoaN3 che3-su7 boe7-oe7 tit-tioh8 hok-khi3 si7 hun-beng5. 
  Lun7 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5, i-e5 chou2-kong i2- keng si2, taN tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7, chiah boe7-oe7 hou7 se3-siok8 lang5 hui2-pong3? Chiau3 goa2 phah-sng3, chou2-kong pe7-bu2 ki3-jian5 si2, sng3-si7 se3-kan e5 tai7-chi3 i2-keng beng5-pek8; lan2 choe3 kiaN2-sun e5 pun2-hun7 iah8 beng5- pek8, boe7-oe7 koh eng7 sim2-mih8 mih8 lai5 hok8-sai7--e5, hou7 i tit-tioh8 li7-ek. Tok8-tok8 ti7 siN-cheng5 e5 si5, tioh8 pi2 se3-siok8 lang5 ka- pe7 iu2-hau3. Sui-bong2 lang5 lam7-sam2 hui2- pong3, si7 bo5 iau3-kin2; na7-si7 the2-thiap i-e5 cheng5, ng3-bang7 khah oe7 in2-chhoa7 i, chiu7 tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 kong2, ¡§Ti7 hoat-goa7 e5 lang5, goa2 oh8--i lai5 kiu3 hoat- goa7 e5 lang5;¡¨ iau2-ku2 oh8 in chhai7 bok8- chu2 lai5 che3-su7, che tek-khak m7-thang. Chong2-si7 iah8 u7 nng7-hang7 e5 hoat-tou7 thang hian2-beng5 lan2 iah8 u7 tui3-tiong7 chou2-kong, hou7 in khah bo5 oe7 thang hui2- pong3. Chit8-hang7, chiu7-si7 chio3 pe7-bu2 e5 siong7, a2-si7 ui7 siau2-eng2, eng7 choa2 lai5 pe3, kui3 ti7 thiaN-lai7, hou7 au7-tai7 e5 kiaN2-sun tit-tioh8 thang khoaN3-kiN3 lai5 siau3-liam7. Na7-si7 tak8-ni5 kau3 i ke3-si3 e5 jit8, chiu7 ke-lai7 e5 si7-toa7-lang5 tioh8 chu7-chip8 i-e5 kiaN2-sun, chiong chou2-kong e5 siong7 hou7 in khoaN3, chiong chou2-kong e5 sou2-kiaN5 ka7 in kong2; che iah8 thang choe3 siau3-liam7 chou2-kong chit8-hang7 e5 hoat-tou7. Chong2-si7 chit- hang7 bo5 put-chi2 un2-tang3; in-ui7 kiaN- liau2 au7-lai5 e5 kiaN2-sun bo5 chiau3 to7-li2, chiu7 khi3 hok8-sai7 chit e5 siong7. 
  Te7-ji7 hang7; chiu7-si7 hian7-si5 Tiong-kok i2-keng u7 chok8-phou2 e5 hoat-tou7; sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 tak8-ke thang ka-ki7 siat chit8 pun2 chok8-phou2, siong5-se3 ki3 chou2-kong siN- cheng5 e5 iong5-mau7, kiaN5-choe3, chhut-si3 ti7 sim2-mih8 si5, si2 ti7 sim2-mih8 si5, bai5-chong3 ti7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7. Tak8-ni5 kau3 i ke3-ong2 e5 jit8, ke-lai7 e5 si7-toa7-lang5 chiu7 chu7-chip8 i-e5 kiaN2-sun, tai7-seng choe3 le2-pai3, hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 beng5-pek8, chiah thak8 chok8- phou2 hou7 i-e5 kiaN2-sun thiaN. 
